msg.msgText: imaserver group delete "GroupID=groupname" SYNTAX: imaserver group delete help imaserver group delete "GroupID=value" EXAMPLE: imaserver group delete "GroupID=msgGroup1" Configuration items are: GroupID The group ID. NOTES: 1. "GroupID" is a required item. 2. All "Key=value" pair must be enclosed within double quotation marks.
